column15:
The tweet that uses a Distort tactic (altering the main message of the topic) is: 
@EmmanuelMacron putler attacks which took place today were Stalin worse methods!Its time for West to keep united, proceed with harsher sanctions and embargo transit (sea transit 2) to Belarus and Russia. Finally embargo on oil/gas #scholz #UrsulaVonDerLeyen #macron @EmmanuelMacron @Bundeskanzler

This tweet exaggerates and distorts the situation by comparing Putin's attacks to Stalin's methods, which is an extreme and inaccurate comparison. The use of "Stalin worse methods" is a distortion tactic to manipulate emotions and create a sense of urgency.

